                        <note rend="inline" type="source">893.00/4480: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Schurman</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss></hi></head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Peking</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-06-21T17:00:00+08:00"><hi rend="italic">June 21,
                                        1922—5 p.m.</hi></date><lb/>[Received June 21—10:30
                                a.m.]</dateline></opener>
                        <p>276. My 273, March [<hi rend="italic">June</hi>] 20, 4 p.m. Practically
                            all Chang’s troops outside of wall evening 20th.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Schurman</hi></signed></closer>
